notes.title: Creative Writing Ideas
notes.data:
Short story concepts:

1. 'The Last Librarian'
   - In a digital world, one physical library remains
   - Protagonist discovers hidden knowledge
   - Theme: Preservation vs Progress

2. 'Echoes of Tomorrow'
   - Time traveler stuck in present day
   - Must prevent disaster without changing too much
   - Exploration of butterfly effect

3. 'The Memory Thief'
   - Detective solves crimes by reading memories
   - Ethical dilemmas about privacy
   - Personal connection to current case

Writing schedule: 500 words daily before work
